REMARKS : Alien species with primarily circumtropical distribution (
Zenetos et al. 2010
). Originally described from Sydney, Australia and now widely distributed around the world. Reported for the first time in the Mediterranean Sea at Naples ( Italy , Tyrrhenian Sea) (
Zibrowius 1992
).

